    <title>Hexo Fluid 内容渲染测试指南</title>
    <link href="/2025/05/17/Fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2025/05/17/Fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文用于测试 Hexo Fluid 主题的内容渲染能力，验证 Markdown语法与扩展功能的正常运作。</p><hr /><h2 id="一代码块测试">一、代码块测试</h2><h3 id="基础代码高亮">1. 基础代码高亮</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">fibonacci</span>(<span class="hljs-params">n</span>):<br>    a, b = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> _ <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(n):<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">yield</span> a<br>        a, b = b, a + b<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">list</span>(fibonacci(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)))<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="行内代码测试">2. 行内代码测试</h3><p>使用 <code>console.log('Hello Fluid')</code> 测试行内代码样式</p><hr /><h2 id="二数学公式测试">二、数学公式测试</h2><h3 id="行内公式">1. 行内公式</h3><p>质能方程：<spanclass="math inline"><em>E</em> = <em>m</em><em>c</em><sup>2</sup></span></p><h3 id="块级公式">2. 块级公式</h3><h2 id="行内公式测试">行内公式测试</h2><p>相对论质能方程：<spanclass="math inline"><em>E</em> = <em>m</em><em>c</em><sup>2</sup></span>，洛伦兹因子：<spanclass="math inline">$\gamma = \frac{1}{\sqrt{1 - v^2/c^2}}$</span></p><h2 id="块级公式测试">块级公式测试</h2><p><span class="math display">$$\sum_{i=0}^n i^2 = \frac{(n^2+n)(2n+1)}{6}$$</span></p><h2 id="矩阵测试">矩阵测试</h2><p><span class="math display">$$\begin{bmatrix}a &amp; b \\c &amp; d\end{bmatrix}\times\begin{bmatrix}e \\f\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}ae + bf \\ce + df\end{bmatrix}$$</span></p><hr /><h2 id="三流程图测试">三、流程图测试</h2><h3 id="mermaid-流程图">1. Mermaid 流程图</h3><div class="mermaid"></div><h3 id="序列图">2. 序列图</h3><div class="mermaid"></div><h3 id="甘特图">2. 甘特图</h3><div class="mermaid"></div><hr /><h2 id="四标签与分类测试">四、标签与分类测试</h2><h3 id="标签显示验证">1. 标签显示验证</h3><ul><li>预期结果：本文应显示 <code>测试</code> 和 <code>Markdown</code>两个标签</li><li>实际显示位置：文章标题下方标签区域</li></ul><h3 id="分类验证">2. 分类验证</h3><ul><li>预期结果：本文应归类至 <code>技术测试</code> 分类</li><li>实际显示位置：网站分类导航菜单</li></ul><hr /><h2 id="五复杂排版测试">五、复杂排版测试</h2><h3 id="嵌套列表">1. 嵌套列表</h3><ol type="1"><li>一级列表<ul><li>二级圆点</li><li>另一个二级项<ul><li>三级加号</li></ul></li></ul></li><li>回到一级</li></ol><h3 id="混合排版">2. 混合排版</h3><p><strong>粗体文字</strong> 与 <em>斜体文字</em> 的组合：</p><blockquote><p>引用区块中的 <code>代码</code> 与 <spanclass="math inline"><em>E</em> = <em>m</em><em>c</em><sup>2</sup></span>公式</p></blockquote><hr /><h2 id="测试结果记录">测试结果记录</h2><table><thead><tr><th>测试项目</th><th>预期效果</th><th>实际结果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Python 代码高亮</td><td>黄色语法高亮，带行号</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>行内公式</td><td>正确显示小字号公式</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Mermaid 流程图</td><td>显示带箭头的流程图</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>标签显示</td><td>显示 2 个蓝色标签按钮</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>嵌套列表</td><td>三级缩进结构清晰</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><hr /><h2 id="问题排查指南">问题排查指南</h2><h3 id="代码不高亮">❌ 代码不高亮</h3><ol type="1"><li>检查主题配置： <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">highlight:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">line_number:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>运行生成命令： <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="公式不显示">❌ 公式不显示</h3><ol type="1"><li>确认文章 Front-matter 包含 <code>mathjax: true</code></li><li>检查主题配置： <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">math:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">engine:</span> <span class="hljs-string">mathjax</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 或 katex</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="流程图不渲染">❌ 流程图不渲染</h3><ol type="1"><li>安装必需插件： <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install hexo-filter-mermaid-diagrams<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>添加主题配置： <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">mermaid:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;9.1.3&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><blockquote><p>测试完成后可删除本文，或保留作为版本更新时的基准测试文档 ```</p></blockquote><h3 id="模板特点">模板特点：</h3><ol type="1"><li>移除所有非内容相关测试项（评论/搜索/统计等）</li><li>强化内容元素的边界测试：<ul><li>代码块嵌套在列表项中</li><li>混合粗体/斜体/引用格式</li><li>复杂公式排版</li></ul></li><li>包含即时验证表格，方便快速记录结果</li><li>配置问题与解决方案一一对应</li><li>所有测试项均无需第三方服务接入<script>     var codes = ["\ngraph TD\n    A([开始]) --> B{条件判断}\n    B -->|条件1| C[操作1]\n    B -->|条件2| D[操作2]\n    C --> E[[结束]]\n    D --> E\n    subgraph 子图模块 [示例]\n        C --> F{二次判断}\n        F -->|是| G[执行]\n        F -->|否| H[跳过]\n    end\n","\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant 客户端\n    participant 服务器\n    客户端->>服务器: 登录请求\n    Note right of 服务器: 验证凭证\n    服务器-->>客户端: 200 OK\n","\ngantt\n    title 项目计划 (兼容模式)\n    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD\n    section 阶段A\n    任务1       :done,    des1, 2025-01-01, 7d\n    任务2       :active,  des2, after des1, 5d\n    section 阶段B\n    任务3       :         des3, 2025-01-15, 3d\n"];     for(var i = 0; i <= codes.length - 1; i++) {       document.querySelectorAll('.mermaid')[i].innerHTML = codes[i];     }   </script><script src="https://unpkg.com/mermaid@7.1.2/dist/mermaid.min.js"></script><script>     if (window.mermaid) {       mermaid.initialize({"version":"7.1.2","enable":true,"theme":"forest","logLevel":5,"startOnLoad":true,"arrowMarkerAbsolute":false,"flowchart":{"htmlLabels":true,"useMaxWidth":true,"curve":"linear"},"sequence":{"diagramMarginX":50,"diagramMarginY":10,"actorMargin":50,"width":150,"height":65,"boxMargin":10,"boxTextMargin":5,"noteMargin":10,"messageMargin":35,"mirrorActors":true,"bottomMarginAdj":1,"useMaxWidth":true},"gantt":{"titleTopMargin":25,"barHeight":20,"barGap":4,"topPadding":50,"leftPadding":75,"gridLineStartPadding":35,"fontSize":11,"fontFamily":"\"Open-Sans\", \"sans-serif\"","numberSectionStyles":4,"axisFormat":"%Y-%m-%d"},"class":{},"git":{}});     }   </script></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
